reviewText: Hollywood romances are all about the beginning of true love.  This movie shows the ending of a true love relationship. Very sweet, but bittersweet. Aging isn't fun but it gives our true character a chance to shine.  Theres a real twist at the end.
Loved this movie, can appreciate and understand it if you are a bit older, touching, made me cry
This is one of the best movies I've seen in awhile.
